notes.text:
This update for php7 provides the following fix:

Security issues fixed:

- CVE-2018-7584: Fixed stack-based buffer under-read while parsing an HTTPresponse in the php_stream_url_wrap_http_ex (bsc#1083639).

Bug fixes:

- Fix a memory leak in the pg_escape_bytea function of the pgsql extension. (bsc#1076970)
